## {background-image="assets/img/planets.jpg" background-size="cover" background-opacity="0.75"}

<h1> A New Era </h1>
<h2> Shiny-based Clinical Submissions using WebAssembly </h2>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<h3> Eric Nantz </h3>
<h3> Eli Lilly & Company </h3>
